title: Jeff Glucker (Hooniverse)
description: Jeff Glucker of Hooniverse stops by to get his card punched, we talk about our time with the GT500, the new Accord, Switzer GT-R, Renntech vs. Brabus, Tom's Alaskan Adventure and Thad gets his car towed.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
